{"tid":610401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳特朗普不滿亞馬遜 或改變其稅務待遇","createTime":"2018-03-30T01:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T06:15:36.000Z","uid":20058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dddca3fa22e0a11990fd3918f3f5754126888f8f","tid":610401,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"【傳特朗普不滿亞馬遜】<br />\n【或改變其稅務待遇】<br />\n<br />\n政治網站 Axios 引述消息指，美國總統特朗普不滿亞馬遜，損害實體零售界利益，尋求改變亞馬遜的稅務待遇。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，特朗普的朋友曾經投訴亞馬遜的電子商貿業務，令他們的業務受損，亦會令商場和商鋪逐漸被淘汰。特朗普其後曾私下討論過，以反壟斷法來追究亞馬遜。<br />\n<br />\n路透社亦引述白宮官員證實，特朗普曾私下批評亞馬遜，認為公司變得太過強大。<br />\n<br />\n並且認為亞馬遜行政總裁貝索斯，擁有的《華盛頓郵報》，是亞馬遜的喉舌，旨在維護公司的商業利益。<br />\n<br />\n去年特朗普已經多次在 Twitter 發文，批評亞馬遜逃避繳付互聯網稅項。<br />\n<br />\n白宮指報道失實，亞馬遜則拒絕回應。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#特朗普　#不滿亞馬遜　#amazon　#損害　#實體零售界　#利益　#稅務待遇<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/824718781053525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F824718781053525%2F&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=09e85056\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/824718781053525/</a>"},{"pid":"52d02d7f202d947205c11175237eaa8adf37f345","tid":610401,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c48e9fdca493c466ad3387a8e909adf3f09f562","tid":610401,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"呢個情況咪同淘寶逼死零售鋪頭一樣<br />\n長遠唔係好事<br />\n唔知trump 可以點搞？"},{"pid":"37996dac1bd6a06ba008687e7fd640c5cae72bb9","tid":610401,"uid":14449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"侵打擊左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e83f9f9cc5e2ba96e1cf408c92